'''數學文摘'''（{{lang-de|Zentralblatt MATH}}，簡稱：zbMATH），是國際數學領域重要的檢索系統之一，提供[[純粹數學|純粹數學]]及[[應用數學|應用數學]]類別文獻的索引、文摘及評論文章，由[[數學家|數學家]][[理查·科朗特|理查·科朗特]]（{{lang|en|Richard Courant}}）、[[奧托·紐格伯爾|奧托·紐格伯爾]]（{{lang|en|Otto Neugebauer}}）、[[哈那德·玻爾|哈那德·玻爾]]（{{lang|en|Harald Bohr}}）及出版商費迪南·德施普林格（{{lang|en|Ferdinand Springer}}）於1931年創立<ref>{{cite book |first=Norbert |last=Schappacher |chapter=Das Mathematische Institut der Universität Göttingen 1929-1950 |pages=523-551 |editor-last=Sauer |editor-first=K. G. |title=Universität Göttingen unter dem Nationalsozialismus |year=1983 |publisher=Wecker, Dahms, Wegeler |location=München |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mochAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA523&lpg=PA523&dq=%22Das+Mathematische+Institut+der+Universit%C3%A4t+G%C3%B6ttingen+1929-1950%22&source=bl&ots=kdWNP-5Y6E&sig=7xPlYnG5oACzPOKvRuxOlEpfPsg&hl=en&sa=X&ei=lfKWVcjtBsHWoAS69ZSYCg&ved=0CDQQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=%22Das%20Mathematische%20Institut%20der%20Universit%C3%A4t%20G%C3%B6ttingen%201929-1950%22&f=false |access-date=2015-07-08 |archive-date=2019-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190816195030/https://books.google.com/books?id=mochAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA523&lpg=PA523&dq=%22Das+Mathematische+Institut+der+Universit%C3%A4t+G%C3%B6ttingen+1929-1950%22&source=bl&ots=kdWNP-5Y6E&sig=7xPlYnG5oACzPOKvRuxOlEpfPsg&hl=en&sa=X&ei=lfKWVcjtBsHWoAS69ZSYCg&ved=0CDQQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=%22Das%20Mathematische%20Institut%20der%20Universit%C3%A4t%20G%C3%B6ttingen%201929-1950%22&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

奧托·紐格伯爾於文摘第一期的序言寫道：

{{cquote|Zentralblatt für Mathematik und ihre Grenzgebiete aims to publish — in an efficient and reliable manner — reviews of the entire world literature in mathematics and related areas in issues initially appearing monthly. As the name suggests, the main focus of the journal is mathematics. However, those areas that are closely related to mathematics will be treated as seriously as the so-called pure mathematics.}}

（中譯：數學文摘旨在複審整個世界在數學及其相關領域的文獻，並以高效和可靠的方式發布，最初會每月出版一冊。正如其名稱所暗示，該雜誌的主要焦點是數學。然而，那些與數學有密切關係的主題也將被認真對待。）

它曾經於[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]前夕，拒絕刊登一批[[猶太|猶太]]學者的評論，而遭到英美學者的抨擊。他們不只憤然辭職，甚至另起爐灶，開創了[[數學評論|數學評論]]，與數學文摘平分秋色<ref>{{cite book|first=D. H.|last=Lehmer|chapter=A Half Century of Reviewing|pages=265–266|url=http://www.ams.org/samplings/math-history/hmath1-lehmer18.pdf|editor-last=Duren|editor-first=Peter|title=A century of mathematics in America|year=1988|publisher=American Mathematical Society|location=Providence, R.I.|isbn=978-0-8218-0124-6|edition=Repr.|access-date=2015-07-08|archive-date=2017-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170819081144/http://www.ams.org/samplings/math-history/hmath1-lehmer18.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

